00:33:21,613 --> 00:33:27,015
We definitely have in-motion plans to create a merchandise collection for Odyssey, they're happening behind the scenes right now.

618
00:33:27,375 --> 00:33:32,838
I think we wanted to do it day and date, but it was just a small team stretched thin and we had to make the decision that merchandise,

619
00:33:33,378 --> 00:33:38,080
while probably the most exciting part of the game for us and one of the most joyful parts because we like to see the things that we make,

